Package com.taliter.fiscal.device

An API to communicate with fiscal devices.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FiscalDevice
    An interface used to communicate with fiscal devices.
    FiscalDeviceEventHandler
    A handler for events that can be triggered by a fiscal device.
    FiscalDeviceSource
    A FiscalDevice factory.
    FiscalPacket
    A request to or response from a fiscal device.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AbortedFiscalRequestException
    Thrown when a request is aborted.
    FiscalDeviceIOException
    The base class of all fiscal device exceptions.
    FiscalDeviceTimeoutException
    Thrown when a request timeout occurs.
    InvalidFiscalResponseException
    Thrown when an invalid response is received.
